[01:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is instead of you have to switch between multiple different tabs all the time, you can stay into that creative flow, and you can just plug in Higgsfield, and you literally have the Higgsfield interface right within Premiere Pro. So,'

